Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银公主贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士君贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将为银公主献上一票
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要给骑士君投票
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得Elder Sister应该会在两位之中诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Sister？
Commment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  因为我觉得这个没必要急着说明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个制度是每年一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选出一位称得上是我校学生代表的Elder Sister
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Sister  就是姐姐的意思吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让学生自己选出做为模范的最高年级学生的制度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我说这种话有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这可是比学生会长更受人尊敬的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要当选Elder Sister需要得到全校学生的75%以上的票
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,75%…这得票数非常高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如没有达到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无人当选了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那样的话所有的候选人都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将自己的得票自由地让给其他的候选人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:02:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算当选了也没有任何权限对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有任何权限
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过影响力可是非常大的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越听越觉得真是独特的制度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样的人可配不上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  要端庄一些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟你是圣应的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么急是赶什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让千早教我英语和数学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正要去图书室呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  前段时间的期中考试的成绩如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要问她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到要千早特训就该明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…香织理你欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子要是能养成天天学习的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成绩立刻就会好起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天天学习？真不想过这样的生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就得严格教育了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅乐乃  淡雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早姐姐  下周记得来华道部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要插夏季的花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您务必来做一下示范
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,示范由小雅来做不就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪不也喜欢姐姐的花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽  虽然是这样没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  我一定会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  那么就先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊  比翼的两位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比翼？什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说关系特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:05:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在魂魄相交的地方  存在着光和痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛？是指吵架之类的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道  先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是如何代入公式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手指真修长啊  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊  这不是很吊人胃口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说薰子的手  真小巧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  我还是第一次被人这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦  来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初音托我来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是有千早的客人来访
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且珍珠的链还断了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍珠从楼梯上散落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好路过的人们帮我捡了回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗  母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了  因为我很担心你过得好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可也用不着来得这么唐突…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊  千岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让我刮目相看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是吗  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史  能给我也倒一杯红茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从初音那听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像收到了很多投票宣言？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且说不定会当选Elder
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还下不了定论啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有很多适合当Elder的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  千岁啊  一进圣应就变成大姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是的  刚才也正在教我学习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信  这孩子经常因为感冒而休息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里顾得上学习什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在却变得这么优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然来就读圣应没有错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全跟女孩子一样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还交上了那么多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了啊  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用晚餐吗  千早大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天累了  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰衣草  能镇定心神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  香织理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过事先声明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是什么事都懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没跟千早的妈妈直接见过面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许这算不上问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过千早的母亲称呼她为「千岁」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早当时没有否认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不用「母亲」而用「妈妈」称呼她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得  有种强烈的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别扭感？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么千早当时没有否认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时都称呼「母亲」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要改成「妈妈」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…早上好  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过身为睡美人的薰子今天起得可真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗  千早才是起得早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为Elder选举的人气TOP4聚在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TOP4？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都在说这里的四人中的某一位将会成为Elder
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说茉清也收到投票宣言了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一次也没收到过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉清的称号是「王子」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同学们似乎都敬而畏之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:10:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早怎么看被视为Elder候补这件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我个人的角度上来说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为淑女受到赞扬是值得高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就以百合为中心来插花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是难度很高的花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请各位要好好观摩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你的  千岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点好起来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岁  千岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岁！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:24.97,title0,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}少女的恋爱与光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小史  千早怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才老师过来诊断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要先让千早大人休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因大概出自睡眠不足及压力过大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小史
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「千岁」究竟是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千早大人的双胞胎姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来他还有姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜千岁小姐在十岁时就因病去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  难怪千早对优雨放不下心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要顽强振作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则  就没有人保护母亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是不对的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是母亲  只要是母亲说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  现在的我毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个存在与否都无关痛痒的路人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你插花时被花刺伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出你会犯这种错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来并无大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  到底能不能做一个完美的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微刺伤一点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小出血就引起贫血  真是惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸中的大幸是倒在了修身室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没摔伤身子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:40.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：因为修身室的地板是榻榻米，材质较软）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到Elder选举的投票日了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好保重身体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  保重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢关心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史的工作就是侍奉千早大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然千早大人说要作为千岁小姐活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有服从到底
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是千早他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得姐姐拥有真正淑女的气质
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您一定要当上Elder
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  能受到你的赞扬是我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  你要当Elder Sister吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是投票选出的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就应该没有要不要当的说法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…千早希望当选吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早的手指这么修长  为什么还…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早你很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅长英语  数学也很拿手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会教我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连击剑的实力都在我之上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我举棋不定的时候能在背后推我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是千早吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千早对我说我可以继续做七七原薰子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早也做千早自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的我都不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早要留在我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一生都在千早身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了母亲  还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以做回我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  小千  好香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面开始宣布Elder Sister投票结果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点到名字的学生请上来讲台
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行寺茉清
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆濑初音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七原薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妃宫千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  希望让票的同学请宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则请保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将我所有的得票让给我的朋友  七七原薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉清…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是怀着相同心意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  皆濑初音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定把我所有的得票让给妃宫千早同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初音…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你架起我跟优雨之间的桥梁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七原薰子  妃宫千早
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持沉默表示没有让票的意向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的得票同为368票
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我作为学生会长提议
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七原同学  妃宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:22:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提议把她们两位同时选为Elder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请赞成的同学鼓掌以示同意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.70,0:22:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  Elder不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不错吧  有2位Elder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.27,0:22:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本年度的Elder Sister
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.57,0:22:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是七七原薰子  以及妃宫千早
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定由以上两位担任
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次请你多多指教  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
